Package: dockpipe
Version: 0.6.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: bash, docker.io | docker-ce, git
Maintainer: dockpipe maintainers
Description: Run any CLI command in a disposable container—project at /work, removed when it exits.
 dockpipe wires docker run for you: your project at /work, container removed when the
 command exits, optional host step after. Use for tests, linters, one-off tools, or agents.
